<sub><italic>ij</italic></sub>∈{0,1,2} correspond to the number of minor alleles at locus <italic>j</italic> for observation <italic>i</italic>. For each <italic>i</italic>∈{1,…,<italic>n</italic>}, we assume that <bold>X</bold>
